definitions.definition: One who, or that which, injects something.

subdefinitions.definition: One who injects (himself or herself with) psychoactive drugs .

Any of various devices that are used to inject something, as: An apparatus by which a stream of water is forced into a steam boiler . Any of the one or more devices in a fuel injection system that create the spray of fuel .

definitions.definition: An object that realizes a dependency injection .

main_definition: One who, or that which, injects something.
secondary_definitions: ( object-oriented programming ) An object that realizes a dependency injection .
